  text: 'Hi! We want to ensure you enjoy a great experience with the app and with
    controlling playback speed. Could you confirm if this issue happens on the mobile
    app or on other devices? Since you’ve already force closed the app, we also recommend
    clearing the app cache on your device and trying a clean reinstall. You can find
    detailed steps on how to do it here: https://t.co/XRlsg9I86o. A quick device restart
    can also do wonders. Give it a try and let us know how it goes!'
