  text: Hey there! That’s definitely not the experience we’re aiming for, so let us
    look into it 👀 Try the basics first - reinstall the app + try from another device
    + check if the same happens on the web player + try connecting to a (different)
    WiFi network- and if the hiccup's still happening, do let us know, and we'll continue
    with this together 😊
